*Verujem* da će se sve na kraju dobro završiti. (I believe that everything will end well.)

*Verujete* li u horoskop? (Do you believe in horoscope?)

Oni *veruju* da je budućnost neizvesna. (They believe that the future is uncertain.)

*Verujući* u njegove reči, krenuli smo na put. (Believing in his words, we started our journey.)

*Veruje* se da je ona najbolja u svojoj grani. (It is believed that she is the best in her field.)